{"tid":717623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估城市]商場指示牌漏電　8歲女二級燒傷心跳過速","createTime":"2018-06-26T07:36:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T14:01:40.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6c65870f1afd4c76dbada096f917b09a96dbf1f2","tid":717623,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:36:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180626/s00004/1529997084965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180626%2Fs00004%2F1529997084965&d=AUEgvheeUj78fjgBelS1%2FqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4923a23d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180626%2Fs00004%2F1529997084965&h=111170e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180626/s00004/1529997084965</a><br />\n<br />\n不少商場都會設置指示牌，展示商場平面圖，方便顧客尋找不同店舖。但這種指示牌原來暗藏危機，成都一個商場的指示牌日前就突然漏電，觸摸該牌的8歲女童隨即觸電，導致心跳過速及二級燒傷。商場承認事故並願意賠償，但事後未有在指示牌附近放置任何警告標語。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事發在本月15日晚上，8歲女孩小雨隨母親到成都成華SM廣場吃飯後離開。抵達1樓後，小雨出於好奇，摸了扶手電梯旁的指示牌，身體即不受控制地倒下。其張姓母親指女兒雖意識清醒，但一直在哭，並說「媽媽我們快走」。張其後才得知是指示牌漏電，令小雨觸電受傷，情況被商場閉路電視拍下。<br />\n<br />\n小雨當晚在張與商場人員陪同下送院檢查，證實「竇性心動過速」。其後小雨手指出現水泡，大腿則有紅色傷痕。事發一周後覆診時，其心電圖已回復正常，但皮膚二級燒傷，醫生建議定期覆診。商場事後確認小雨因商場指示牌漏電而受傷，向其賠償醫療費166.7元（人民幣，下同）及2000元購物卡以作「慰問」。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒昨再到商場觀察，事發地點已重新設置指示牌。現在接近商場其中一個主要出口，有不少人途經，但指示牌周圍未見提醒有可能漏電等的警告標語。商場未有回應指示牌漏電原因，或事後有無檢查或維修相關設備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180626/s00004/4d37bd4ac061a52484b0f5fffd9dbf95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180626%2Fs00004%2F4d37bd4ac061a52484b0f5fffd9dbf95.jpg&h=c1b0850f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45bd3f7d26627d0db229b89125dbf7c0dd9fcfba","tid":717623,"uid":26752,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:52:44.000Z","msg":"SM廣場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46105a910a56d2b370520ba11dd0ec14146eec93","tid":717623,"uid":3340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:54:41.000Z","msg":"仲以為係香港，估錯左添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d731873f9990533356360bd139d8a05d06feff13","tid":717623,"uid":163492,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"其賠償醫療費166.7元（人民幣，下同）及2000元購物卡以作「慰問」。"},{"pid":"59b2329edb0e8d70f1c04dce54c3e40732e1c514","tid":717623,"uid":175896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d731873f9990533356360bd139d8a05d06feff13","tid":717623,"uid":163492,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"其賠償醫療費166.7元（人民幣，下同）及2000元購物卡以作「慰問」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:01:11.000Z","msg":"阿媽fatfat買個手袋先"},{"pid":"76f546df8ce98d6b53ac476de1585c3b9cc301d6","tid":717623,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d731873f9990533356360bd139d8a05d06feff13","tid":717623,"uid":163492,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"其賠償醫療費166.7元（人民幣，下同）及2000元購物卡以作「慰問」。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"2000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地俾乞兒都500啦"},{"pid":"5fe970311807cf1b585d77db2154f4bbf9c28d91","tid":717623,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76f546df8ce98d6b53ac476de1585c3b9cc301d6","tid":717623,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d731873f9990533356360bd139d8a05d06feff13","tid":717623,"uid":163492,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"其賠償醫療費166.7元（人民幣，下同）及2000元購物卡以作「慰問」。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"2000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/sm